2. Software bundled into the published container images
--------------------------------------------------------

The Go license scan does not see container contents; this section is the
manual ledger for the images Cloister publishes to GHCR.  Base images that
deployments merely PULL from their upstream registries (ollama/ollama,
alpine/socat) are not redistributed by this project and are not listed.

ghcr.io/jeffbstewart/cloister-agent
  Bundles qwen-code and its Node.js runtime, from the base image
  ghcr.io/qwenlm/qwen-code.
    qwen-code — Apache License 2.0
      https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code/blob/main/LICENSE
    Node.js — MIT (with bundled-component licenses)
      https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/main/LICENSE
  The base image's own license and notice files are retained unmodified
  inside the published image.

ghcr.io/jeffbstewart/cloister-workers
  A scratch-based image: the Apache-2.0 cloister-worker binary plus the
  Mozilla CA certificate bundle (copied from Alpine's ca-certificates
  package at build time; nothing else of Alpine ships).
    Mozilla CA certificate data (from NSS) — Mozilla Public License 2.0
      https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/

ghcr.io/jeffbstewart/cloister-builder-jvm
  Bundles Amazon Corretto 25 (a distribution of OpenJDK), from the base
  image amazoncorretto:25.
